The Cheneys are reportedly a close family, and even Liz's dad, former Vice President Cheney, has said of gay marriage, "I think people ought to be free to enter into any kind of union they wish. . . . I think freedom means freedom for everyone." Given all this, it would seem that Liz is bucking the family on this one, as well as hurting her sister.
